What is the work of Cell 9?

Cell 9 does not create the RDF triples.

Its only job is:

Understand the meaning of the sentence and extract the semantic relationship (predicate) between the Source XML page and the linked XML page.

Think of Cell 9 as a Relation Extraction step.

Example 1

Source XML

Title:
Turbine Engineering

Sentence from Cell 8

Turbine Engineering is a team within HotEnd Design.

Hyperlink

HotEnd Design

Cell 9 should output

{
    "subject": "Turbine Engineering",
    "predicate": "within",
    "object": "HotEnd Design"
}
