Your XML example

Suppose your XML contains

Title

Turbine Engineering

Content

Turbine Engineering is a team within
[[HotEnd Design>>doc:wiki:Temp_Import.HotEndDesign.WebHome]]

under

[[Turbomachinery>>doc:wiki:Temp_Import.Turbomachinery.WebHome]]

Cell 8 produces

Sentence

Turbine Engineering is a team within HotEnd Design under Turbomachinery.

Now Cell 9 asks the LLM:

What relationship connects

Turbine Engineering

and

HotEnd Design

LLM returns

within

Again

What relationship connects

Turbine Engineering

and

Turbomachinery

LLM returns

under
Output of Cell 9

The output should be something like this:

semantic_records = [

{
"subject":"Turbine Engineering",
"predicate":"within",
"object":"HotEnd Design"
},

{
"subject":"Turbine Engineering",
"predicate":"under",
"object":"Turbomachinery"
},

{
"subject":"HotEnd Design",
"predicate":"contains",
"object":"Blade Design"
}

]

Notice that Cell 9 is only producing semantic relationships.
